    • isLock

      public boolean isLock()
      Returns true if registry is locked; false otherwise. If the registry is locked, songs cannot be retrieved or added outside the registry.
      Returns:
      true if the registry is locked; false otherwise.

    • reload

      public void reload(@Nonnull NonnullConsumer<Integer> andThen)

      Parameters:
      andThen - - Consumer of how many songs was loaded to execute after the load.

    • byName

      @Nullable public Song byName(@Nonnull String name)

      Returns:
